### API Integration Test File
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tool
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Ping
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ping
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Ready
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

###

### List All Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Accept: application/json

###

### List Accounts with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Account (replace with valid ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Account Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "count": 5
}

###

### Generate Accounts (Multiple Jobs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/generate
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "count": 3,
  "priority": "normal"
}

###

### Update Account (replace with valid ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "active",
  "notes": "Updated via API"
}

###

### Delete Account (replace with valid ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/1

###

### List All Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Accept: application/json

###

### List Jobs with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?limit=20&offset=0
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Job (replace with valid UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Cancel Job (replace with valid UUID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

###

### Get Job Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Overall Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### WebSocket Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/ws/stats
Accept: application/json

